dct_description_sm: Longitudinal and latitudinal lines (Greenwich and Ferro meridians).
Color legend shows German, Austro-Hungarian, and Russian territories (also showing administrative divisions within these territories).
Legend shows canals, forts, fortresses, cities, villages, various roads, railroads, mines, monasteries, churches/chapels.
Dated from title and presence of "Oesterreich-Ungarn" territory.
